Package student

Class Student

java.lang.Object
student.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Student>
Direct Known Subclasses:
NonResident, Resident
public abstract class Student extends Object implements Comparable<Student>
Handles the Student object which contains profile object, major enum and credit completed. Student object is the object that is used for roster management.
Author:
Raghunandan Wable, Srikumar Avirneni
